responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "E370F3CB4423DEC69F20F097E6F04361", "It may not be for certain, but he\'s our best hope yet. He\'s brought us grace in a time of crisis, and it\'s a welcome respite from our daily struggles. I hardly remember more than a few occasions when someone of his stature toured the common districts.")
